{"type": "article", "id": 22626, "title": "方形霓虹桌灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142333zGTxlQHet0i7RIWa.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是美国设计工作室 SPIN-R 带来的一款方形的 LED 灯 Tittle，它含有 512 个小的节点，可以与智能手机相连来控制灯的颜色、亮度以及变化的模式，产生出类似霓虹灯的效果。灯体小巧而色彩绚丽，是调节气氛的小工具。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/tittle-light-the-captivating-3d-led-smart-lamp#/\">这里是众筹链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061423311UQFY6VE8Lqf23IM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142331dgs5tIKDXkyvLNeW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142332QjcoFGemshyRY1HK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142332rFthLjS16aWopOUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142332hSIpbJPNQq1DEHr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}